{
  "id": "1As7j6fB",
  "slug": "enhanced-world-creation",
  "title": "Enhanced World Creation",
  "description": "Adds more settings when creating a world and allows to apply saved settings",
  "body": "<a href='https://ko-fi.com/X8X71FI3YO' target='_blank'><img height='36' style='border:0px;height:36px;' src='https://i.postimg.cc/SQ5ZLKg5/support-me-on-kofi-beige.png' border='0' alt='Buy Me a Coffee at ko-fi.com' /></a>\n\n## Enhanced World Creation\n\nThis mod expands the world creation screen and adds settings for changing its default \nparameters.\n\n![preview](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f205ad5f695cb4c84de991b06fb0467c543f87b4.jpeg)\n\n## Usage\n\nA new button will appear during world creation. Clicking it will open a screen where you can add an icon for the world and install a built-in resource pack. This resource pack will be automatically applied to the player upon entering the world.\n\n![preview](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e44d408195a84f9d65b2169c760a72baceb35d2a.jpeg)\n\nThe mod has a configuration option. In its settings, you can set the default parameters for world creation. This will significantly speed up the process if you frequently generate new worlds.\n\n![preview](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ec79550b6606e0602e33e8e66a1dbfd9dffdba89.jpeg)\n\nI don't plan to add default game rules or data packs. Mods already exist for that.",
